Javascript and WebGL demo.
Simulation of fire (particle system) within a dark room (walls with dynamic lighting).

Check live version:
http://www.disturbedcoder.com/files/DarkRoom/

Third party libraries:
gl-matrix (https://github.com/toji/gl-matrix)
stats.js (https://github.com/mrdoob/stats.js)

Information:
After cloning this repository, to properly run the HTML file you must enable your browser for local access:
- Firefox: go to "about:config" and modify "security.fileuri.strict_origin_policy" to false.